import React from "react";
import {

  Container,
  Form,
  FormControl,
  Nav,
  Navbar,
  NavDropdown,
} from "react-bootstrap";
import {Link} from 'react-router-dom'
const Header = () => {
  return (
    <Navbar bg="primary" expand="lg" variant="dark">
      <Container>
      <Navbar.Brand href="/">the_list</Navbar.Brand>
        <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbarScroll" />
        <Navbar.Collapse id="navbarScroll">
          <Nav className="m-auto" navbarScroll>
            <Form inline>
              <FormControl
                type="search"
                placeholder="Search"
                className="me-2"
                aria-label="Search"
              />
            </Form>
          </Nav>
          <Nav>
            
          <Navbar.Brand href="/">My Lists</Navbar.Brand>
            <NavDropdown title="Basil Breton" id="navbarScrollingDropdown">
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#action4">My Profile</NavDropdown.Item>
              <NavDropdown.Divider />
              <NavDropdown.Item href="#action5">Logout</NavDropdown.Item>
            </NavDropdown>
          </Nav>
        </Navbar.Collapse>
      </Container>
    </Navbar>
  );
};

export default Header;
